snippet.title: Crazy Plant Shop | Filament Learning
snippet.description: Crazy Plant Shop is a plant genetics learning game aligned to middle school science standards. Become a floral entrepreneur as you breed wacky plants! Use a magic Punnett square machine to determine dominant and recessive traits so you can fulfill customer orders, learning about trait inheritance and plant genetics.
